SELECT r.id AS "runs.id",
    r.track AS "runs.track",
    t.id AS "tracks.id",
    t.manual_id AS "tracks.manual_id",
    t.name AS "tracks.name",
    t.name_ja AS "tracks.name_ja",
    t.name_en AS "tracks.name_en",
    t.name_cn AS "tracks.name_cn",
    t.name_cht AS "tracks.name_cht",
    tv.id AS "track_versions.id",
    tv.track_id AS "track_versions.track_id",
    tv.version AS "track_versions.version",
    tv.name AS "track_versions.name",
    r.category AS "runs.category",
    r.date AS "runs.date",
    r.date_str AS "runs.date_str",
    r.player AS "runs.player",
    r.time AS "runs.time",
    r.board AS "runs.board",
    cb.id AS "characters.board.id",
    cb.manual_id AS "characters.board.manual_id",
    cb.name AS "characters.board.name",
    cb.name_ja AS "characters.board.name_ja",
    cb.name_en AS "characters.board.name_en",
    cb.name_cn AS "characters.board.name_cn",
    cb.name_cht AS "characters.board.name_cht",
    r.rider AS "runs.rider",
    cr.id AS "characters.rider.id",
    cr.manual_id AS "characters.rider.manual_id",
    cr.name AS "characters.rider.name",
    cr.name_ja AS "characters.rider.name_ja",
    cr.name_en AS "characters.rider.name_en",
    cr.name_cn AS "characters.rider.name_cn",
    cr.name_cht AS "characters.rider.name_cht",
    r.video_status AS "runs.video_status",
    r.video_type AS "runs.video_type",
    r.video_url AS "runs.video_url",
    r.replay_file AS "runs.replay_file",
    r.note AS "runs.note"

FROM runs r
LEFT JOIN tracks t ON r.track = t.id
LEFT JOIN characters cb ON r.board = cb.id
LEFT JOIN characters cr ON r.rider = cr.id
LEFT JOIN track_versions tv ON r.track = tv.track_id AND r.track_version = tv.version

ORDER BY t.manual_id ASC,
    r.category ASC,
    r.date DESC,
    r.time ASC;
